import React from 'react'
import Footer from '../Components/Footer'
import Nabvar from '../Components/Nabvar'
import User from '../Components/User'
import AddUser from '../Components/AddUser'


export default function Login() {

  
  return (
   <>
   <Nabvar></Nabvar>
     
     <User></User>
   <AddUser></AddUser>

   <Footer></Footer>
   </>
  )
}
